e-mindfulness-in-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":16119,"position":2},"title":"How to achieve mindfulness in Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 2, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Whoever is mindful of Allah Almighty in his thoughts, Allah will protect him in his limbs.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Worship \u0639\u0628\u0627\u062f\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Worship \u0639\u0628\u0627\u062f\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/worship-ibadah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22840,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/held-accountable-thoughts\/","url_meta":{"origin":16119,"position":3},"title":"Are we held accountable for our thoughts?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 14, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Allah has pardoned my nation for what occurs within themselves...\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/wisdom-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13376,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/an-nawawi-on-the-virtue-of-love-for-the-sake-of-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":16119,"position":4},"title":"Imam al-Nawawi on Love for the Sake of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 2, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Where are those who love each other for My sake?\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24261,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/forty-hadith-on-muraqaba\/","url_meta":{"origin":16119,"position":5},"title":"Forty Hadith on Mindfulness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Excellence is to worship Allah as if you see Him,\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16119","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=16119"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16119\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=16119"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=16119"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=16119"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}